data.description:
Serene Value in Convenient North Central location. Flexible Loft Space for Office/4th Bedroom! Soaring ceilings & unique architecture. Open Kitchen w/ plentiful Granite counter space & walk in Pantry. Be transported in your peaceful tiered backyard! Pavers + Flagstone walkways add charming detail & spacious seating areas in which to relish the romantic Tuscan element of slender cypress & lion's head fountain.  Enjoy the solitude this private location provides! Sip a drink in the shade of a rare red oak; and experience changing seasonal colors. Mechanically sound! Roof, Plumbing, Electrical systems all well maintained by caring long time owner! Baths updated w/ travertine style shower surrounds. Neutral tile. Handy powder room. Clean epoxy garage! Highly efficient commercial AC. Energy Saving Sunscreens
Diagonally Laid Tile
French Door Entry to Primary Bedroom
Walk in Closet at Primary Bedroom
Super Efficient and Quiet AC
